description:
We are currently looking for **React Native Developers** to join our team.

Please, watch a video recorded by our CEO Viktor Jarnheimer that fully describes our requirements and current opportunities: [https://vimeo.com/500037831](http://vimeo.com/500037831)

**Our perfect candidate has:**
* 5+ years of commercial experience;
* 2+ years of React Native experience; 
* Excellent English level (Upper-intermediate or higher);
* Entrepreneurial mindset;
* You are on high level and is supposed to make many decisions by yourself, often as the only React Native developer in the team. 

**Your impact:**
* Have the main responsibility for the front-end; 
* Transform designs from Sketch into the application, with pixel perfection.

